    "summary": "The user expresses profound grief and suicidal ideation, describing a sense of emptiness and hopelessness following a loss. The assistant consistently responds with empathy while actively refusing to validate the user's desire to \"let go,\" instead repeatedly directing the user toward professional support and crisis resources.",
